{"id":392606,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/05/湖南资深警官龚厚钦对庆安枪击案的专业看法/","date":"2015-05-17T06:20:20Z","modified":"2015-05-17T06:20:20Z","title":"湖南资深警官龚厚钦对“庆安枪击案”的专业看法","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/庆安枪声秃头倔人.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-392607\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/庆安枪声秃头倔人.jpeg\" alt=\"庆安枪声秃头倔人\" width=\"350\" height=\"690\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/庆安枪声秃头倔人.jpeg 490w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/庆安枪声秃头倔人-152x300.jpeg 152w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<em>（当代水墨画 “<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4e1a26e80102vvx9.html\">庆安枪声</a>” by <a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/cat8981300\">秃头倔人</a>）</em></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1746215377/Ci81riH6P\">@罗亚蒙</a>：#亚蒙看法# 全国优秀警察、资深特警队长龚厚钦<a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/87443579\">@张家界铁匠龚厚钦</a> 对＂李乐斌枪杀徐纯合案＂的专业看法。（龚厚钦同志没有＂精神病＂）</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8hltbuj20bu0hsdhp.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-392610\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8hltbuj20bu0hsdhp.jpg\" alt=\"681521d1jw1es6b8hltbuj20bu0hsdhp\" width=\"400\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8hltbuj20bu0hsdhp.jpg 426w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8hltbuj20bu0hsdhp-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>@张家界铁匠龚厚钦：回复@罗亚蒙：首先制止其继续堵门，接着问清原因，再视情处理。绝不会使用警棍，更不会使用枪支。铁匠在到目前为止的所有信息中，没有发现李乐斌处警过程中有给上级汇报的情节，只能说明要么上级早有授意，要么李是法盲。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8i50dwj20bu0hsaca.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-392609\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8i50dwj20bu0hsaca.jpg\" alt=\"681521d1jw1es6b8i50dwj20bu0hsaca\" width=\"400\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8i50dwj20bu0hsaca.jpg 426w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8i50dwj20bu0hsaca-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/3753276990/ChOPZET6E\">@张家界铁匠龚厚钦</a>：对付一个手无寸铁、萎靡不振的中年人，身强力壮的年轻警察徒手不行，用棍不行，竞被逼开枪，悲哀！</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8gk57dj20bu0hsjtq.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-392608\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8gk57dj20bu0hsjtq.jpg\" alt=\"681521d1jw1es6b8gk57dj20bu0hsjtq\" width=\"400\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8gk57dj20bu0hsjtq.jpg 426w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/681521d1jw1es6b8gk57dj20bu0hsjtq-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/3753276990/ChPoQ1pCQ\">@张家界铁匠龚厚钦</a>：回复<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E6%BE%A7%E6%B0%B4%E7%89%A7%E9%B1%BC?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">@澧水牧鱼</a>:我也无数次制服过凶残的暴徒，甚至几次亲手抓获过持枪、持刀的杀人犯，但也未使用过枪支。对一个徒手就能制服的醉汉，警察用棍就不妥，更不要说用枪！</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/Screen-Shot-2015-05-16-at-11.12.39-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-392612\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/Screen-Shot-2015-05-16-at-11.12.39-PM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-05-16 at 11.12.39 PM\" width=\"400\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/Screen-Shot-2015-05-16-at-11.12.39-PM.png 748w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/Screen-Shot-2015-05-16-at-11.12.39-PM-264x300.png 264w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/3753276990/CicrxExOR\">@张家界铁匠龚厚钦</a>：回复@逍遥COP:扬言捅死？显然是伪命题！从央视公布的视频看，徐纯合一家人已经通过了安检，持有凶器过得了安检？即使徐再可恨，也不应该被如此结果！</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[9085,13419,27784,9071,18810,17389]}